The 'thumb-piano' and 'musical bow' are now as rare in Zambia as they were once common! A selection from Hugh Tracey's historical recordings of these wonderful 'little' musics - sometimes extrovert, sometimes meditative.

Historical recordings by Hugh Tracey.
